Package: gdalraster.windows
Title: Windows GDAL Runtime and gdalraster Bootstrap Tools
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jimmy", "Briggs", , "jimmy.briggs@jimbrig.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7489-8787"))
Description: Installs and activates a self-contained GDAL runtime on
    Windows and provides helpers to install gdalraster from source against
    that GDAL instead of the default Rtools GDAL.
